#if soper
Command provided by: groupserv/set_pubacl
#endif
Help for SET PUBACL:

SET PUBACL, when enabled, permits any and all users to view
the FLAGS, TEMPLATE, and TEMPLATEVHOST lists for the group.
Otherwise, the ability to view the flags list (holding flag
+A) is required.

Syntax: SET <!group> PUBACL <ON|OFF>

Examples:
    /msg &nick& SET !TestGroup PUBACL ON